lead_paragraph: Genzebe Dibaba set a women’s world record in the indoor mile in Stockholm on Wednesday, beating a record that had stood for 26 years. Dibaba, an Ethiopian, was timed in 4 minutes 13.31 seconds.

headline.main: Genzebe Dibaba Sets Indoor Mile Record
